title: Millencolin - Use your nose
description:
Use Your Nose is the first EP by the Swedish punk rock group Millencolin, released on December 4, 1993 by Burning Heart Records. All of the songs from the EP were re-released on the 1999 compilation album The Melancholy Collection.
